 hydrous ethanol, including rectified spirit, denatured spirit, ethanol, organic manure, potash rich ash, and fusel oil. It also exports its products. The company was formerly known as Siel Limited and changed its name to Mawana Sugars Limited in January 2008. Mawana Sugars Limited was incorporated in 1961 and is based in Gurugram, India."}}